snippet.title: Johnny Depp VS Amber Heard Shocking Domestic Abuse Allegations
snippet.description:
Source:
https://www.spreaker.com/user/robinlynne/johnny-depp-vs-amber-heard-shocking-dome

Shawn Johnson, Olympic gold medalist and winner of Dancing With The Stars joins us to talk about her amazing life in the spotlight and how she handles the pressure of the big moment. But first, Senior Reporter Chloe Melas, Fashion Director Katrina Mitzeliotis and Producer @GinoOrlandini talk about the shocking domestic violence allegations against Johnny Depp from his wife Amber Heard. Plus, Rob Kardashian and Blac Chyna are taking the biggest step in their relationship yet - they're getting their own reality show.
